OL,6,     FNew. Helen McNicoll: Fiona Bruce
OL,7,     Fand Philip Mould investigate when
OL,8,     Fart dealer David Taylor believes
OL,9,     Fhe's found a work by Helen
OL,10,     FMcNicoll, one of Canada's most
OL,11,     Fcelebrated impressionists.
OL,12,G2200 Bangers & Cash
OL,13,     FThunderbird / Citroen SM / Punto /
OL,14,     FBMW: Derek travels to the
